00274                                           !BCC_ASM
00275                                           MACRO SET_INT_VECTOR
00276                                             push ds
00277                                             xor ax, ax
00278                                             mov ds, ax
00279                                             mov ax, ?3
00280                                             mov ?1*4, ax
00281                                             mov ax, ?2
00282                                             mov ?1*4+2, ax
00283                                             pop ds
00284                                           MEND
00285

00355                       00000106            vgabios_init_func:
00356                                           
00357                                           ;; init vga card
00358 0106           E8         306F              call _init_vga_card
00359                                           
00360                                           ;; init basic bios vars
00361 0109           E8         308C              call _init_bios_area
00362                                           
00363                                           
00364 010C           E8         6593              call _vbe_has_vbe_display
00365 010F           3C                     00    cmp al, #0x00
00366 0111           74           03              je init_no_vbe_display
00367                                           
00368                                           ;; init vbe functions
00369 0113           E8         65AA              call _vbe_init
00370                                           
00371                       00000116            init_no_vbe_display:
00372                                           
00373                                           
00374                                           ;; set int10 vect
00375                                             SET_INT_VECTOR(0x10, #0xC000, #vgabios_int10_handler)
 +a   0116           1E                           push ds
 +a   0117           31C0                         xor ax, ax
 +a   0119           8ED8                         mov ds, ax
 +a   011B           B8                   0145    mov ax,  #vgabios_int10_handler
 +a   011E           A3         0040              mov 0x10*4, ax
 +a   0121           B8                   C000    mov ax,  #0xC000
 +a   0124           A3         0042              mov 0x10*4+2, ax
 +a   0127           1F                           pop ds
00376                                           
00377                                           ;; display splash screen
00378 0128           E8         30E4              call _display_splash_screen
00379                                           
00380                                           ;; init video mode and clear the screen
00381 012B           B8                   0003    mov ax,#0x0003
00382 012E           CD                     10    int #0x10
00383                                           
00384                                           ;; copy and activate 8x16 font
00385 0130           B8                   1104    mov ax, #0x1104
00386 0133           B3                     00    mov bl, #0x00
00387 0135           CD                     10    int #0x10
00388 0137           B8                   1103    mov ax, #0x1103
00389 013A           B3                     00    mov bl, #0x00
00390 013C           CD                     10    int #0x10
00391                                           
00392                                           ;; show info
00393 013E           E8         30CF              call _display_info
00394                                           
00395                                           
00396                                           ;; show vbe info
00397 0141           E8         65C4              call _vbe_display_info
00398                                           
00399                                           
00400                                           
00401 0144           CB                           retf
00402                                           !BCC_ENDASM
00403                                           ! 275 
00404                                           ! 276 
00405                                           ! 277 
00406                                           ! 278 
00407                                           ! 279 #asm
00408                                           !BCC_ASM
00409                       00000145            vgabios_int10_handler:
00410 0145           9C                           pushf
00411 0146           06                           push es
00412 0147           1E                           push ds
00413 0148           60                           pusha
00414                                           
00415                                           ;; We have to set ds to access the right data segment
00416 0149           BB                   C000    mov bx, #0xc000
00417 014C           8EDB                         mov ds, bx
00418 014E           E8         3104              call _int10_func
00419                                           
00420 0151           61                           popa
00421 0152           1F                           pop ds
00422 0153           07                           pop es
00423 0154           9D                           popf
00424 0155           CF                           iret
00425                                           !BCC_ENDASM

13531 3178           BA                   03C2    mov dx, #0x3C2
13532 317B           B0                     C3    mov al, #0xC3
13533 317D           EE                           outb dx,al
13534

13538 3183           EE                           outb dx,al
13539

13543 3189           EE                           outb dx,al

13562                                           ! 331 static void init_bios_area()
13563                                           ! 332 {
13564                       00003198            _init_bios_area:
13565                                           ! 333 
13566                                           ! 334   write_word(0x40,0x10,read_word(0x40,0x10)&0xFFCF);
13567 3198           55                         push	bp
13568 3199           89E5                       mov	bp,sp
13569 319B           B8                   0010  mov	ax,*$10
13570 319E           50                         push	ax
13571 319F           B8                   0040  mov	ax,*$40
13572 31A2           50                         push	ax
13573 31A3           E8         2DB1            call	_read_word
13574 31A6           89EC                       mov	sp,bp
13575 31A8           24                     CF  and	al,#$CF
13576 31AA           50                         push	ax
13577 31AB           B8                   0010  mov	ax,*$10
13578 31AE           50                         push	ax
13579 31AF           B8                   0040  mov	ax,*$40
13580 31B2           50                         push	ax

13582 31B6           89EC                       mov	sp,bp
13583                                           ! 335 
13584                                           ! 336 
13585                                           ! 337

13589 31BB           50                         push	ax

13591 31BF           50                         push	ax

13595 31C7           89EC                       mov	sp,bp
13596                                           ! 340 
13597                                           ! 341

13600 31CC           50                         push	ax
13601 31CD           B8                   0087  mov	ax,#$87

22766                                           
22767 64C3                      0146            .word 0x146
22768 64C5                      0100            .word 0x100
22769 64C7                      4100            .word 0x100 + 0x4000
22770 64C9                      0101            .word 0x101
22771 64CB                      4101            .word 0x101 + 0x4000
22772 64CD                      0103            .word 0x103
22773 64CF                      4103            .word 0x103 + 0x4000

22775 64D3                      4105            .word 0x105 + 0x4000
22776 64D5                      FFFF            .word 0xFFFF
22777                                           
22778                                           
22779                                           !BCC_ENDASM
22780                                           ! 131 
22781                                           ! 132 
22782                                           ! 133 
22783                                           ! 134 
22784                                           ! 135 #asm
22785                                           !BCC_ASM
22786                                           MACRO HALT
22787                                             ;; the HALT macro is called with the line number of the HALT call.
22788                                             ;; The line number is then sent to the 0x501, causing Bochs to
22789                                             ;; print a BX_PANIC message. This will normally halt the simulation
22790                                             ;; with a message such as "BIOS panic at rombios.c, line 4091".
22791                                             ;; However, users can choose to make panics non-fatal and continue.
22792                                             mov dx,#0x501
22793                                             mov ax,#?1
22794                                             out dx,ax
22795                                           MEND
22796                                           !BCC_ENDASM
22797                                           ! 147 
22798                                           ! 148 
22799                                           ! 149 
22800                                           ! 150 static Bit16u dispi_get_id()
22801                                           ! 151 {
22802                                           
22803                       000064D7            _dispi_get_id:
22804                                           ! 152   outw(0xFF80,0x0);
22805 64D7           55                         push	bp
22806 64D8           89E5                       mov	bp,sp
22807 64DA           31C0                       xor	ax,ax
22808 64DC           50                         push	ax
22809 64DD           B8                   FF80  mov	ax,#$FF80
22810 64E0           50                         push	ax
22811 64E1           E8         FADC            call	_outw
22812 64E4           89EC                       mov	sp,bp
22813                                           ! 153   return inw(0xFF81);
22814 64E6           B8                   FF81  mov	ax,#$FF81
22815 64E9           50                         push	ax
22816 64EA           E8         FAB8            call	_inw
22817 64ED           89EC                       mov	sp,bp
22818 64EF           5D                         pop	bp
22819 64F0           C3                         ret
22820                                           ! 154 }
22821                                           ! 155 
22822                                           ! 156 static void dispi_set_id(id)
22823                                           ! 157   Bit16u id;
22824                       000064F1            _dispi_set_id:
22825                                           ! 158 {
22826                                           ! 159   outw(0xFF80,0x0);
22827 64F1           55                         push	bp
22828 64F2           89E5                       mov	bp,sp
22829 64F4           31C0                       xor	ax,ax
22830 64F6           50                         push	ax
22831 64F7           B8                   FF80  mov	ax,#$FF80
22832 64FA           50                         push	ax
22833 64FB           E8         FAC2            call	_outw
22834 64FE           89EC                       mov	sp,bp
22835                                           ! 160   outw(0xFF81,id);
22836 6500           FF76         04            push	4[bp]
22837 6503           B8                   FF81  mov	ax,#$FF81
22838 6506           50                         push	ax
22839 6507           E8         FAB6            call	_outw
22840 650A           89EC                       mov	sp,bp
22841                                           ! 161 }
22842 650C           5D                         pop	bp
22843 650D           C3                         ret

22942                                           ! 193 {

22944 6586           55                         push	bp
22945 6587           89E5                       mov	bp,sp
